Joe Starr GULLAHORN v. C. H. LOONEY, Warden, United States Penitentiary, Leavenworth, Kansas. No. 5832. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. May 14, 1958. No appearance for appellant. William C. Farmer, U. S. Atty., Topeka, Kan., and Milton P. Beach, Asst. U. S. Atty., Kansas City, Kan., for ap-pellee.

Before MURRAH, PICKETT and LEWIS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed without written opinion.
